---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About | Logo Brief Guide" pathname="/about/">
  <section class="prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Why this site exists</h1>
    <p>
      Logo Brief Guide exists to help people make smarter logo decisions before
      they spend money. The goal is simple: better briefs, clearer expectations,
      fewer wasted purchases.
    </p>
    <p>
      This is not a design agency. It is a practical guide for buyers who want to
      compare options, ask better questions, and avoid common mistakes.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
